'''本戈河'''（{{lang-pt|''' Rio Bengo'''}}），又称'''Zenza'''，是[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]西北部的一条河流，发源于[[水晶山脉_(非洲)|水晶山脉]]，流入大西洋[[本戈湾|本戈湾]]，全长约300km，流域面积约7370km<sup>2</sup>。河口位于[[本戈省|本戈省]]，[[罗安达|罗安达]]以北约20km处。

本戈河上建有Kiminha水库，<ref>[http://www.fao.org/docrep/005/t0473e/t0473e01.htm Source book for the inland fishery resources of Africa...] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fao.org/docrep/005/t0473e/t0473e01.htm |date=20140109063052 }}, FAO</ref>河流冲积平原的下游90km也有几个小湖泊，如Panguila、Quilunda和Lalama。本戈河冲积平原是罗安达主要的粮食产地。<ref>[https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-adv/specialsales/spotlight/angola/article16.html The Province Of Bengo: Manna from Muxima] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-adv/specialsales/spotlight/angola/article16.html |date=20201021062556 }}, ''Washington Post''</ref>1889年修建引水渠之前，罗安达的饮用水也是通过装桶用船运输的。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=IMwNAAAAQAAJ&pg=PA15&lpg=PA15&dq=bengo+river+angola&source=bl&ots=Wjpgzps91W&sig=9xC4xrLcS2QYcBj731ivh_861so&hl=en&sa=X&ei=aCPOUqXrCNDvoATL0oLoCw&ved=0CEgQ6AEwBTgK#v=onepage&q=bengo%20river%20angola&f=false Angola and the River Congo, Volume 2], Joachim John Monteiro, Macmillan and Company, 1875, p. 15-19</ref>现代则从河中用水泵抽水，再用卡车运输。<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/16/world/africa/16cholera.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 In Oil-Rich Angola, Cholera Preys Upon Poorest] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/16/world/africa/16cholera.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |date=20180102191350 }}, SHARON LaFRANIERE, ''New York Times'', June 16, 2006</ref>

本戈河河口生长有红树林，接近其生长南界。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=wzSCkulW9SQC&pg=PA241&lpg=PA241&dq=zenza+river+angola&source=bl&ots=jfsdP_wGxS&sig=wcjHxzCkL2vzMu5BquYSxIsXB4E&hl=en&sa=X&ei=tiXOUuqzH4v7oATB5oGIDw&ved=0CEgQ6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=zenza%20river%20angola&f=false ''World Atlas of Mangroves''], Mark Spalding, Mami Kainuma and Lorna Collins, Earthscan, 2010, p 241.</ref>河中有鳄鱼、海牛、鸭、鱼类等动物生活。河中发展的[[水产养殖|水产养殖]]业只有[[罗安达省|罗安达省]][[Kifangondo|Kifangondo]]的[[罗非鱼|罗非鱼]]养殖场。<ref>[http://omap.africanmarineatlas.org/BIOSPHERE/data/fishes/fisheries/CountryCatches/Fishery%20Country%20Profiles/FAO%20Fishery%20Country%20Profile%20-%20Angola.htm Fishery Country Data: Angola] {{Wayback|url=http://omap.africanmarineatlas.org/BIOSPHERE/data/fishes/fisheries/CountryCatches/Fishery%20Country%20Profiles/FAO%20Fishery%20Country%20Profile%20-%20Angola.htm |date=20160303225016 }}，联合国粮农组织</ref>

本戈河周边地区曾发生过多场战役。1641年荷兰人[[荷属卢安果-安哥拉|占领罗安达]]期间葡萄牙人撤退。1873年本戈河和丹德河之间的[[登博斯|登博斯]]人起义反抗葡萄牙统治。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=BKKf4PYI-IIC&pg=PA312&lpg=PA312&dq=zenza+river+angola&source=bl&ots=vq5U0Ry8BH&sig=INXm4OjxOBLdNnO4RObaPar3YWo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=gCbOUrXdLIfeoASnpIHwAQ&ved=0CFgQ6AEwCDgK#v=onepage&q=zenza%20river%20angola&f=false ''The Creole Elite and the Rise of Angolan Protonationalism: 1870-1920''], Jacopo Corrado, Cambria Press, 2008, p. 35.</ref>1975年的{{link-en|Battle of Quifangondo}}是[[安哥拉独立战争|安哥拉独立战争]]中的一场重要战役。

